.RS

Acknowledge an action error on the node. An acknowlegment can be completed by --author (defaults to root@nodename) and --comment

.TP
.B --author=AUTHOR
The acker name to log when acknowledging action log errors
.TP
.B --comment=COMMENT
A comment to log when acknowldging action log error entries.
.TP
.B --color=COLOR
